Mythril -(https://github.com/ConsenSys/mythril)
requirements:
need to install python(current version/ 3.0+)
need to install pip
need to install Rust/Cargo (nightly)

Errors:
Works well with my laptop(not sure what i downloaded to make it work), but does not work in my primary pc. Gives the error 'Running setup.py install for pyethash ... error' 
i suspect i need to download an updated version of rust / cargo, but still gives error.


Manticore - (https://github.com/trailofbits/manticore)
Requirements: 
need to install python(current version/ 3.0+)
need to install pip
need to install solc
need to install z3
need to install Rust/Cargo (nightly)

For macusers:
need to install Homebrew



